v>\n                    <h3>Mobile Ready</h3>\n                    <p>Works perfectly on all devices and screen sizes</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    \n    <script src=\"script.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>",
